    },
    {
      "id": "637178",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "elsaanna",
        "uid": "24409"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t人均gdp 10000元是假的，李克强都说了一半人收入不到1000，平均也就是人均月入2000，合5000人均gdp\t\t</div>",
